{"tid":1387902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"be water be條撚(唔該真係入黎睇一睇)","createTime":"2019-07-30T15:25:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T16:13:08.000Z","uid":12970,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"338f82c08edcf09e6ee7cd0b8645ecf0fa831af3","tid":1387902,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:25:20.000Z","msg":"講明先我都唔係一個咩人<br />\n你當我係冷氣軍師又好<br />\n我都係講下自己意見<br />\n最近都已經係連登見過無數關於留守嘅問題<br />\n我覺得要認真探討一下<br />\n打游擊戰撤退係咪代表失敗主義<br />\n係唔係一直留守先代表真正勇武<br />\n當然有情況係趕唔切撤退唔計<br />\n<br />\n但係一直留守等到人哋增援到<br />\n又拉多幾個義士<br />\n唔係一句尊重前線決定就啱<br />\n戀戰嘅諗下你嘅決定後果可能係你隔離嗰個承擔<br />\n成日be water有邊次真係真正做到<br />\n勇武唔代表可以有勇無謀<br />\n諗下多一個被捕嘅義士對成場運動影響係點<br />\n就係少左戰力<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n你留守多半個鐘爭取到嘅嘢值唔值得有多幾個義士被補去換取</span></span><br />\n我唔係叫任何人教前線點樣做嘢<br />\n但我相信睇到呢個post嘅人一定有人之前係企係前線或者將來都會<br />\n希望你企喺前線嘅時候諗下<br />\n<br />\n最後利申<br />\n現場嘅情況交翻比前線決定<br />\n只係希望義士真正做到be water<br />\n同埋要知道任何決定嘅風險都係所有義士同你一齊承擔"},{"pid":"7db471f900666ddbd525df0825904573f7df20f7","tid":1387902,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:26:12.000Z","msg":"Be water"},{"pid":"4603c7578be7ed4093f45cf762cccd5ddac2803a","tid":1387902,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:26:26.000Z","msg":"Be water"},{"pid":"15d4a948d7b1926def7b43e4bd8539fc16d444e3","tid":1387902,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:26:39.000Z","msg":"Be water"},{"pid":"e049c5849116428d888673bd5f679024e653a660","tid":1387902,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:26:49.000Z","msg":"對得住前線！對得住義士！<br />\n一日政府無回應 一日都要繼續抗爭！<br />\n一個都不能少！<br />\n堅持五大訴求！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">也試過太衝動 大件事沒計輕重<br />\n錯過悔過仍要衝 衝出困局<br />\n形象似義勇軍<span style=\"color: violet;\">(crusade)</span>般英勇<br />\n但結果有沒有停戰的溝通?<span style=\"color: violet;\">(訴求？)</span><br />\n如戴著面具<span style=\"color: violet;\">(mask)</span>去掩飾倦容<br />\n迎著炮火也依然表情輕鬆<span style=\"color: violet;\">(不屈？)</span><br />\n情緒不可激動 還若輕的舉重<br />\n來化解一切壓力似失蹤<br />\n如放下面具去也許面紅<span style=\"color: violet;\">(憤怒？)</span><br />\n乘著晚風去追尋逍遙星空<br />\n除去假的寬容 還真想不通<br />\n曾年少的青蔥 懷著理想那怕痛<span style=\"color: violet;\">(revolution)</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TfDAuxC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTfDAuxC.png&h=60385d7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gnOwNja.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgnOwNja.png&h=f5b7bc3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"7e7e6432c286ccb1b7569004f39f00a16e379f37","tid":1387902,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:26:50.000Z","msg":"Hit and run"},{"pid":"8621b51e87d34344214f76eea6775b1923fcf2b8","tid":1387902,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:27:01.000Z","msg":"留守"},{"pid":"582eb904f9b163cfbe8b58f7f66e21d9b993d6fc","tid":1387902,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:27:20.000Z","msg":"Be water"},{"pid":"b9823f66031448722a03ee567379bccdb23a29a4","tid":1387902,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:27:32.000Z","msg":"Be water"},{"pid":"294810209786be09f9def3f64460610958c43acc","tid":1387902,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:27:45.000Z","msg":"睇下都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74fd21d414562dec55127d7b9630182a7